visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: display
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Ewert

designer: Multiple Designers

approved: true
description: <p>Ewert is slab serif wood type inspired \
  by and loosely based on the collection of cultural \
  infographic maps by Estonian graphic artist Olev Soans. \
  Ewert has been higly simplified for screen usage yet \
  still includes the characteristic "ornamental leg" \
  of the letterform.</p> \
  <p>Ewert was designed by Johan Kallas and Mihkel Virkus.</p>

font.Ewert-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Ewert-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

